snippet.title: Roblox Wednesday Roleplay - Enid is Jealous of Xavier?
snippet.description: Wednesday the Show is still a fan favorite. Let's Roleplay with Wednesday Characters like Enid and Xavier. In this Roblox episode Wednesday is driving home from nevermore when she gets a text from Enid. They end up spending the day together shopping and all the things Enid loves but Wednesday Despise. In effort to escape she goes to the coffee shop and sees Xavier working there. She ends up talking to him and forgets about Enid. Enid gets so Jealous because she thinks Wednesday ditched her. Will this damage their friendship? Does Wednesday have a crush on Xavier? lets find out in this fun roleplay. This episode is Family friendly for all Wednesday fans.
